Step 1:
PC-A -> Services -> NTP
Enable it 
Key 1
Password NTPpa55

Step 2:
R1,R2,R3 ->(everything in step 2 in all the routers)
write en and conf t (opens config)
Router(config)# ntp server 192.168.1.5
Router(config)# ntp update-calendar

Step 3:
R1,R2,R3 ->(everything in step 3 in all the routers)
